pinput.description: Pin code input (OTP) text field, iOS SMS autofill, Android SMS autofill One Time Code, Password, Passcode, Captcha, Security, Coupon, Wowcher, 2FA, Two step verification

dismissible_page.description: Creates page that is dismissed by swipe gestures, with Hero style animations, Inspired by Facebook, Instagram stories.
